## 5-Layer Architecture (Final)

```
Layer 1: EXTRACT — separate detailed_facts from author_rhetoric
                    ↓
Layer 2: TRANSFORM — generate alternative_rhetoric from facts
                    ↓
Layer 3: CODE SANITIZE — strip author_rhetoric before outline + writer see it
                    ↓
Layer 4: OUTLINE — depth_focus MUST come from alternative_rhetoric (new angle)
                    ↓
Layer 5: WRITER — first paragraph MUST develop depth_focus before specs
```

## Risk Assessment (All Niches)

| Niche | Mode | Risk | Protected by |
|-------|------|------|-------------|
| **Firearms** | Review | ⚠️ HIGH | ✅ 5-layer system |
| **Military** | Review | ⚠️ HIGH | ✅ 5-layer system |
| **Mystery** | Review | 🟢 LOW | Extract discards rhetoric (rules 11-12), 7 structures × 4 closings × tone arc |
| **Biography** | Narrative | 🟢 LOW | 8 structures × 6 closings, framework restructure, personal profile enrichment |
| **Battle** | Narrative | 🟢 LOW | Framework restructure, scene construction from raw data |

## Not Changed (Evaluated and Rejected)

- **Spec-dump → Experiential writing**: Evaluated but rejected — risk of AI exaggeration/fabrication outweighs benefit. Spec-first is safer for factual accuracy.
- **Mystery anti-plagiarism**: Not needed — structural diversity provides natural protection.
- **Narrative anti-plagiarism**: Not needed — framework restructure + personal profile + scene construction provides natural protection.
